# Track the system structure, NOT harvested buyer data or client-sensitive output.

# Raw harvested buyer language (may contain client/PII data)
*/data/raw/*
!*/data/raw/.gitkeep

# Per-source extractions (derived from raw)
*/data/extracted/*
!*/data/extracted/.gitkeep

# Generated outputs (real buyer profiles, real prospects)
*/output/*
!*/output/.gitkeep

# Filled memory (priors learned from real data) — keep schema, ignore contents
*/memory/patterns.md

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
